<span style="font-weight: bold;">Wait, isn't this a free site?</span>

<br><br>

<div style="margin-left: 40px;">
You might ask yourself, why donate to Divineprophecy.org?  The
site is free, right?  Well, we are a non-profit organization and
our site might be available to everyone at no cost as a public
good, but that doesn't mean that it doesn't cost money to build,
support and improve.  That's why we're asking you to support us and
our work.

<br><br>

Just to give you an idea of the kinds of things that we need to
support, here's a small list of some of the expenses we incur in a
regular basis:

<ol>

  <li>Cost to host and test this website.</li>

  <li>Database space for the forum, roster, and image storage</li>

  <li>Places for the developers to sit.</li>

  <li>Software licenses for the software used in development.</li>

</ol>

Remember, your donation will support an excellent, free, and informational
website.  Do your part and keep the site open.

</div>

<br>

